title: Pressing launch wont open league
body: When i turn on league i get the free champions and stuff and the launch button. when i press it nothing  happens. i tried deleting lol_patcher and lol_launcher but it dosent work and when i check it again lol_patcher and lol_launcher is back there

replies.body:
This issue occurs if your connection to the login servers is poor. Incompatible local network settings is the most common culprit for this, so I'd recommend working through our [connection guide](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues), as it should resolve this.

Let me know the results of those steps.
